{"tid":1590034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想為呢場運動輕生嘅你麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:18:23.000Z","uid":305696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f91981c69bed5df048bd22be9b220c4f281b968","tid":1590034,"uid":305696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"P牌勿屌<br />\n話說本人係海狗做緊野<br />\n跟住今日收到一個咁樣嘅message<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNsERi2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNsERi2.jpg&h=f9a6fad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近排係連登成日見到好多類似「我想了結自己生命」呢種post<br />\n於是我見到呢條message 之後就有左咁樣嘅諗法：<br />\n如果睇緊呢個post嘅你 冇工開 冇學返 覺得自己一無事處 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n同我入海洋公園做臥底！！！！！！！</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我日日full gear返工！！！！！！！！</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是係10月1日！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊賀佢老母！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">If we burn, you burn with us!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"8eb03c5d6fea5e232f359cfd69b353d7915a25df","tid":1590034,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY